"Gala Dal\u00ed, Marchioness of Dal\u00ed de P\u00fabol (born Elena Ivanovna Diakonova; 7 September [O.S. 26 August] 1894 \u2013 10 June 1982), usually known simply as Gala, was the Russian wife of poet Paul \u00c9luard and later of artist Salvador Dal\u00ed, who were both prominent in surrealism. She also inspired many other writers and artists."